reply.reply: Dojo Room is a Ford Cloud Platform tool that allows users to schedule sessions [3]. It is accessed through the Ford Cloud Portal [3]. Project configuration is stored in the GCP Project GitHub Organization [3]. Users can create new projects, update existing projects, and add new environments [3]. They can also update GCP services, delete or destroy GCP projects, and schedule Dojo sessions [3].
